div.p:
“During the course of the present phase of the negotiations two governments, as announced in Washington and Moscow on _____,Omission in the original. have reached agreement on the following:
“1. Agreement on measures to reduce the risk of outbreak of nuclear war between the United States of America and the Union of Soviet Socialist Republics;
“2. Agreement between the United States of America and the Union of Soviet Socialist Republics on measures to improve the USA–USSR direct communications link.
